{"data":{"post":{"id":"f92d6b78-add5-53c1-b395-3f5ff210d061","html":"<div>\n          <div\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper\"\n            style=\"padding-bottom: 56.29139072847682%; position: relative; height: 0; overflow: hidden;margin-bottom: 2em\"\n          >\n            <iframe allowfullscreen frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/Yob2uziCHaQ?feature=oembed\" style=\"\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n          \"></iframe>\n          </div>\n          </div>\n<p>\n  <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n  \n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7ff831c6425be77fb43bbd37a0bcb676/b8d06/post-cucaracha_junlxf.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 124px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 112.90322580645163%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"post-cucaracha\"\n        title=\"post-cucaracha\"\n        src=\"/static/7ff831c6425be77fb43bbd37a0bcb676/b8d06/post-cucaracha_junlxf.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7ff831c6425be77fb43bbd37a0bcb676/b8d06/post-cucaracha_junlxf.jpg 124w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 124px) 100vw, 124px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">post-cucaracha</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p>Después de varios años sin poder recordar el título de este video que encontrareis a continuación, hace un par de dias mi primo Mauro me lo recordó! (se llama “creepshow”) y aquí lo pongo, para que todos lo sufrais. Quizás es una razón importante del asco que le tengo a las cucarachas…</p>","fields":{"slug":"/la-invasion-de-las-cucarachas/","prefix":"27 February 2009"},"frontmatter":{"title":"La invasión de las cucarachas","category":"film","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/7ff831c6425be77fb43bbd37a0bcb676/d927d/post-cucaracha_junlxf.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/la-invasion-de-las-cucarachas/","prev":{"id":"a4d46577-766e-57c2-abab-13ccd119af2b","fields":{"slug":"/la-tumba-de-las-luciernagas/","prefix":"2009-02-09","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"La Tumba de las Luciérnagas","category":"film"}},"next":{"id":"6f68badd-3137-55de-8f81-162b0f85aabb","fields":{"slug":"/los-videojuegos-desarrollan-la-inteligencia/","prefix":"2009-03-01","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Los videojuegos desarrollan la inteligencia","category":"games"}},"source":"posts"}}